Name: Unknown
Description: Unknown size or the instruction doesn't reference any memory (eg. #(c:LEA)#)

Name: SegPtr16
Description: Memory location contains a seg:ptr pair, #(t:u16)# (offset) + #(t:u16)# (segment/selector)

Name: SegPtr32
Description: Memory location contains a seg:ptr pair, #(t:u32)# (offset) + #(t:u16)# (segment/selector)

Name: SegPtr64
Description: Memory location contains a seg:ptr pair, #(t:u64)# (offset) + #(t:u16)# (segment/selector)

Name: WordOffset
Description: Memory location contains a 16-bit offset (#(c:JMP/CALL WORD PTR [mem])#)

Name: DwordOffset
Description: Memory location contains a 32-bit offset (#(c:JMP/CALL DWORD PTR [mem])#)

Name: QwordOffset
Description: Memory location contains a 64-bit offset (#(c:JMP/CALL QWORD PTR [mem])#)

Name: Fword6
Description: Memory location contains a 16-bit limit and a 32-bit address (eg. #(c:LGDTW)#, #(c:LGDTD)#)

Name: Fword10
Description: Memory location contains a 16-bit limit and a 64-bit address (eg. #(c:LGDTQ)#)

Name: FpuEnv14
Description: Memory location contains a 14-byte FPU environment (16-bit #(c:FLDENV)#/#(c:FSTENV)#)

Name: FpuEnv28
Description: Memory location contains a 28-byte FPU environment (32/64-bit #(c:FLDENV)#/#(c:FSTENV)#)

Name: FpuState94
Description: Memory location contains a 94-byte FPU environment (16-bit #(c:FSAVE)#/#(c:FRSTOR)#)

Name: FpuState108
Description: Memory location contains a 108-byte FPU environment (32/64-bit #(c:FSAVE)#/#(c:FRSTOR)#)
